          %h1 Personal Protective Equipment (PPE) P.O. Financing and Funding
        %p Due to the global impact of  Covid-19, Personal Protection Equipment (PPE) which partially includes gloves,  masks, gowns, and sanitizers is in critical demand worldwide. Governmental agencies, hospitals, and long-term care facilities are receiving priority for these scarce resources.
