        %p.highlighted
          Gateway Commercial Finance has developed
          %strong Special PPE Funding Solutions
          to eligible manufacturers and distributors of Personal Protective Equipment products. These Special Funding Solutions may include Trade Funding, PPE Purchase Order Finance and Receivables Funding or a combination of services to support product/delivery fulfillment.
        %h2
        %h2 How do PPE Financing and PPE Factoring Work
        %p.highlighted We can support businesses through PPE Letters of Credit, Vendor Guarantees, or wire transfer upon delivery and inspection of goods at a U.S. port of entry (via ocean or air freight). In special circumstances, we may consider providing down payment to well-qualified third-party suppliers.
        %ul
          %li PPE Funding from $250K to $5MM;
          %li New account set-up as fast as 4 business days*;
          %li Transactional/On-going Fulfilment funding;
        %p *assumes no current lending relationship
        %h2 How to Qualify for PPE Funding
        %p Eligible candidates must demonstrate the following:
        %ol
          %li Experience in medical supply manufacturing/distribution;
          %li Creditworthy end-buyers;
          %li History of supply chain management (domestic/international);
          %li Manufacturers/Suppliers must have appropriate FDA or similar product credentialing which can be verified;
          %li Third-party inspection required;
        %p
          Most clients utilizing
          %strong Special PPE Funding Solutions
